---
title: "SSD UC3 — Listen to Story Narration (TTS)"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC3 — Listen to Story Narration

    User->>S: openStory(storyId)
    S-->>User: storyData(title, scenes[], pdfPath)

    User->>S: selectVoice(voice: "male" | "female")
    S-->>User: voiceSelected(voice)

    loop for each scene page user navigates to
        User->>S: requestNarration(storyId, sceneNumber, voice)

        alt audio already cached
            S-->>User: audioReady(audioPath, cached: true)
        else audio not cached
            S-->>User: audioGenerating(sceneNumber)
            S-->>User: audioReady(audioPath, cached: false)
        end

        User->>S: playAudio(audioPath)
        S-->>User: audioPlaying(duration)

        opt user pauses
            User->>S: pauseAudio()
            S-->>User: audioPaused(position)
        end

        opt user resumes
            User->>S: resumeAudio(position)
            S-->>User: audioPlaying(duration)
        end
    end
